flowchart TD
    A[Agent Startup] --> B[Scan skills/ folders]
    B --> C[For each folder with SKILL.md]
    C --> D[Parse frontmatter<br/>name, description, requires]
    D --> E[Add to Skill Catalog]
    E --> F[Catalog ready]

    F --> G[User request arrives]
    G --> H{Match skill?}
    H -->|Yes| I[Retrieve skill documentation]
    I --> J[Check binary dependencies]
    J --> K{All deps satisfied?}
    K -->|No| L[Instruct user to install<br/>Show install steps]
    K -->|Yes| M[Construct command<br/>from skill patterns]
    M --> N[Spawn external process<br/>(bash/cli)]
    N --> O[Stream output & monitor]
    O --> P[Process completes]
    P --> Q[Return result to user]
    H -->|No| R[No applicable skill<br/>Handle directly or use other tools]
    R --> Q

    subgraph "ClawHub Management"
        S[clawhub search] --> T[Query registry]
        U[clawhub install] --> V[Download & extract to skills/]
        W[clawhub update] --> X[Fetch new version]
    end

    V --> B
    X --> B